an><span style=color:#f6f8fa;background-color:#82071e>%</span><span style=color:#fff> </span><span style=color:#f6f8fa;background-color:#82071e>/</span><span style=color:#1f2328>paige</span><span style=color:#f6f8fa;background-color:#82071e>/</span><span style=color:#1f2328>email</span><span style=color:#fff> </span><span style=color:#f6f8fa;background-color:#82071e>%</span><span style=color:#57606a>}}</span></span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p><p><span class=paige-shortcode-email><a href data-a="ZXhhbXBsZQ==" data-b="QA==" data-c="ZXhhbXBsZS5jb20=" onclick='this.href="mailto:"+atob(this.dataset.a)+atob(this.dataset.b)+atob(this.dataset.c)'>E-mail me</a></span></p>]]></content><id>tag:example.com,0001-01-01:/shortcodes/email/</id><link href="https://example.com/shortcodes/email/" hreflang="en-us" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><published>0001-01-01T00:00:00Z</published><rights type="html">© Will Faught</rights><summary type="html">Demonstration of the email shortcode.</summary><title type="html">Email</title><updated>0001-01-01T00:00:00Z</updated></entry></feed>